@startuml logout_sequence
actor User as U
boundary MenuScreen as Menu
boundary LogoutScreen as Logout
boundary LoginScreen as Login
control LogoutController as LC

U -> Menu: 選択("ログアウト")
activate Menu
Menu -> LC: showLogoutScreen()
activate LC
LC -> Logout: display()
activate Logout
Logout --> LC: displayed
deactivate Logout
LC -> LC: waitForUserConfirm()
note right of LC
 ユーザーがログアウトを選択するまで待つ
end note
U -> Logout: 選択("ログアウト")
activate Logout
Logout -> LC: confirmLogout()
activate LC
LC -> Login: displayLogin()
activate Login
Login --> LC: displayed
deactivate Login
LC --> Logout: logoutCompleted
deactivate LC
Logout --> U: 表示: ログアウト完了
deactivate Logout

@enduml
